videoSnippet.title: 1950s Hamburger Joint! | Caruana vs Gelfand | Batumi Chess Olympiad (2018)

Fabiano Caruana vs Boris Gelfand
43rd Chess Olympiad (2018), rd 5, Sep-28 
Sicilian Defense: Nezhmetdinov-Rossolimo Attack. Fianchetto Variation (B31)
